# Project Structure Guide

This project is organized as follows:

- The main entry point is [src/main.tsx](mdc:src/main.tsx), which bootstraps the application.
- The root React component is [src/App.tsx](mdc:src/App.tsx).
- Frontend code is located in [src/frontend/](mdc:src/frontend), which contains:
  - [pages/](mdc:src/frontend/pages): Top-level pages (e.g., [Notes.tsx](mdc:src/frontend/pages/Notes.tsx), [Files.tsx](mdc:src/frontend/pages/Files.tsx), [Tasks.tsx](mdc:src/frontend/pages/Tasks.tsx), [Timer.tsx](mdc:src/frontend/pages/Timer.tsx), [Calendar.tsx](mdc:src/frontend/pages/Calendar.tsx), [Projects.tsx](mdc:src/frontend/pages/Projects.tsx), and [auth/](mdc:src/frontend/pages/auth) for authentication pages).
  - [features/](mdc:src/frontend/features): Feature modules, each with their own components and hooks (e.g., [notes](mdc:src/frontend/features/notes), [files](mdc:src/frontend/features/files), [tasks](mdc:src/frontend/features/tasks), [timer](mdc:src/frontend/features/timer), [project](mdc:src/frontend/features/project), [calendar](mdc:src/frontend/features/calendar), [auth](mdc:src/frontend/features/auth)).
  - [components/](mdc:src/frontend/components): Shared UI, layout, and theme components (e.g., [ui/](mdc:src/frontend/components/ui), [layout/](mdc:src/frontend/components/layout), [theme/](mdc:src/frontend/components/theme)).
  - [utils/](mdc:src/frontend/utils): Utility functions (e.g., [auth.ts](mdc:src/frontend/utils/auth.ts), [utils.ts](mdc:src/frontend/utils/utils.ts)).
  - [types/](mdc:src/frontend/types): TypeScript type definitions (e.g., [calendar.ts](mdc:src/frontend/types/calendar.ts)).
  - [hooks/](mdc:src/frontend/hooks): Custom React hooks (e.g., [use-mobile.tsx](mdc:src/frontend/hooks/use-mobile.tsx), [use-toast.ts](mdc:src/frontend/hooks/use-toast.ts)).
  - [lib/](mdc:src/frontend/lib): Additional utility libraries (e.g., [utils.ts](mdc:src/frontend/lib/utils.ts)).
- Backend code is located in [src/backend/](mdc:src/backend), with [api/](mdc:src/backend/api) and [types/](mdc:src/backend/types).
- Shared UI components are also available in [src/components/ui/](mdc:src/components/ui).
- Configuration files include [package.json](mdc:package.json), [vite.config.ts](mdc:vite.config.ts), [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts), and TypeScript configs ([tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json), [tsconfig.app.json](mdc:tsconfig.app.json), [tsconfig.node.json](mdc:tsconfig.node.json)).
- The [public/](mdc:public) directory contains static assets.
- The [supabase/](mdc:supabase) directory is for Supabase integration.

Refer to this rule for a high-level overview of the codebase structure.
